            <title>[CASSANDRA-17052] Queries performed with NODE_LOCAL consistency level do not update request metrics</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17052</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, queries performed with &lt;tt&gt;NODE_LOCAL&lt;/tt&gt; consistency level are not reflected in request metrics. The suggested patch addresses that, and also allows modification and batch statements to be used with &lt;tt&gt;NODE_LOCAL&lt;/tt&gt; consistency level.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
